modShortDescription: This mod changes the time in which zombies get up, ranging from 1 to 10 seconds. This will allow players some randomness and a bit of an extra challenge.
modDescription:
This mod changes the time in which zombies get up, ranging from 1 to 10 seconds. This will allow players some randomness and a bit of an extra challenge when in melee, because unless they’re staring at the XP bar, they won’t know for sure if a zombie is down and out or just down, ready to pounce.

[Download](https://gitlab.com/guppycur/guppymods/-/archive/master/guppymods-master.zip?path=Guppycur%27s_Random_ZombieGetterUpper)

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/9144-guppycurs-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Guppycur](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/guppycur/)
